Updating Vehicle tracking system
feat: Update color scheme to purple for consistency across the application

Add initial technical documentation for Vehicle Tracking System
- Created main LaTeX document structure with title, abstract, and table of contents. - Added introduction chapter detailing project overview, background, problem domain, and solution approach. - Included diagrams and tables to illustrate system architecture and technology evolution. - Established formatting and styling for code listings and references.

Add Reports and Simple Reports screens with PDF generation functionality
- Implemented ReportsScreen for generating various types of reports (Trip, Daily, Weekly, Monthly, Safety). - Added UI components for selecting report type and date range. - Integrated PDF generation using PDFReportGenerator service. - Created SimpleReportsScreen for displaying vehicle stats and generating simple PDF reports. - Included recent reports section with sample data. - Enhanced user experience with loading indicators and snack bar notifications for report generation status.

feat: Add user registration screen with vehicle registration options
- Implemented UserRegistrationScreen for user sign-up with phone number. - Added form fields for name, email, vehicle number, and license number. - Included role selection (Driver, Rider/Customer, Fleet Manager) with conditional vehicle registration for drivers. - Integrated success and error feedback via SnackBars. - Created RoutePlanningPanel for route selection with popular locations in Vadodara. - Developed RoutePlanningWidget for turn-by-turn directions with travel mode options and route summary. - Added mock data generation for route options and directions.
